Virgil Security C++ SDK ChangeLog (Sorted per date)

# Version 3.2.1 released 2016-06-21

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.7.0



# Version 3.2.0 released 2016-05-12

## Changes

  * Split VirgilCards to Global scope and Private scope

## Features

  * [Build] Implement in-house package manager based on CMake

# Version 3.1.0 released 2016-04-29

## Features

  * Add custom identities functionality

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.5.0



# Version 3.0.6 released 2016-04-18

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.4.0



# Version 3.0.5 released 2016-04-06

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.4.0-rc1

## Bugfix

  * Add missed code error handle ( 30306 ) for Virgil Keys Service


# Version 3.0.4 released 2016-03-30

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.3.4
  * Fix bug in http::Request - when parameters_ empty added '?'
  * Add IPMessaging in examples
  * Update docs with new template


# Version 3.0.2 released 2016-03-25

## Changes

  * Fix bug: wrong default base address of the Virgil Private Keys Service



# Version 3.0.1 released 2016-03-21

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.3.2.


# Version 3.0.0 released 2016-03-15

## Changes

  * Use virgil-crypto lib 1.3.1.


# Version 3.0.0-RC1 released 2016-02-29

## Changes

  * Merge all SDKs to one.
  * Add Virgil Identity Service API version 1.
  * Add Virgil Keys Service API version 3.
  * Add Virgil Private Keys Service API version 3.

